# DDD Tactical Building Blocks

Internal implementation of domain logic.

## Tactical Elements
- Entity (identity)
- Value Object (immutable)
- Aggregate Root (consistency boundary)
- Domain Service (orchestration)
- Repository (storage interface)

## Anti-Patterns
- Anemic Models
- Leaking Infrastructure logic
- Oversized Aggregates

## Workflows
1. Design Aggregates
2. Create Entities/VOs
3. Implement Domain Logic
4. Wrap with Repositories
